! Map caps to lctrl and vice versa using xmodmap.
! source:
! https://www.jveweb.net/en/archives/2010/11/making-better-use-of-the-caps-lock-key-in-linux.html#jveweb_en_017_03

!Swap Caps Lock with the Left Control key
remove Lock = Caps_Lock
remove Control = Control_L
keysym Caps_Lock = Control_L
keysym Control_L = Caps_Lock
add Lock = Caps_Lock
add Control = Control_L

! run  xmodmap ~/.Xmodmap 
